{% extends "generic/regions.njk" %}
{% block main %}
<main class="c-main">

  <div class="c-section c-section--wild-sand">

    <div class="o-container">

      <ul class="c-listicle">
        <li class="c-listicle__item">
          <svg class="o-icon c-listicle__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation">
            <path d="M12 4c4.41 0 8 3.59 8 8s-3.59 8-8 8-8-3.59-8-8 3.59-8 8-8m0-2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="c-listicle__title">The gender pay gap</h3>
          <p class="c-listicle__description">Full-time working women earn a base salary that is about 17% less, and a total remuneration that is more than 22% less, than full-time working men<sup>4</sup>.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="c-listicle__item">
          <svg class="o-icon c-listicle__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation">
            <path d="M12 4c4.41 0 8 3.59 8 8s-3.59 8-8 8-8-3.59-8-8 3.59-8 8-8m0-2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="c-listicle__title">Maternity leave</h3>
          <p class="c-listicle__description">5 years out of the paid labour force for a woman on average earnings during their early 30s will reduce the eventual retirement account balance by over $80,000<sup>5</sup>.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="c-listicle__item">
          <svg class="o-icon c-listicle__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation">
            <path d="M12 4c4.41 0 8 3.59 8 8s-3.59 8-8 8-8-3.59-8-8 3.59-8 8-8m0-2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="c-listicle__title">Tax concessions</h3>
          <p class="c-listicle__description">The bottom 30% of income earners receive no government tax concessions, while the top 20% of income earners receive $10,000 per year<sup>6</sup>.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="c-listicle__item">
          <svg class="o-icon c-listicle__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation">
            <path d="M12 4c4.41 0 8 3.59 8 8s-3.59 8-8 8-8-3.59-8-8 3.59-8 8-8m0-2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="c-listicle__title">Life span</h3>
          <p class="c-listicle__description">Women typically retire earlier than men and on average live longer, and therefore require more superannuation to retire on comfortably.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="c-listicle__item">
          <svg class="o-icon c-listicle__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation">
            <path d="M12 4c4.41 0 8 3.59 8 8s-3.59 8-8 8-8-3.59-8-8 3.59-8 8-8m0-2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="c-listicle__title">Part-time and casual work</h3>
          <p class="c-listicle__description">Working in part-time or casual capacity leaves individuals with less working hours to build their retirement balance.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <!-- /c-listicle -->

